{
  "stem": "25598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She will give it to him in 10 years' time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If the marriage goes well and he is a good boy, he'll get the dowry after 10 years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But of course, after 10 years-- things have changed very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She actually offered him a dowry after 10 years, which was after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he refused it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this Uncle Armin, who was really very-- he was brought up-- he studied in the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was in the cheder, and he was a terrific merchant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he never had a store or anything, but he was always dealing and wheeling with things, and he always had money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he was actually instrumental in saving our lives when we ended up in camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just, I think that I-- I think everybody thought that life was going to continue the way it was, with on Monday we do this, and on Sunday we do this, and on Friday we do that because that's how the whole town lived.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole town was in this beautiful, peaceful structure of when we go for walks in the park and when we go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was all set.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life started changing in '38.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it changed when anti-Semitism began to be felt more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It changed more in, in '39, and even more in '40, when we were supposed to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were curfews, and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- aside from a few anti-Semitic incidents like the one that start-- that I experienced in school, it didn't affect me, personally, except for the fact that the adults around me were whispering and keeping things away from me.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that those were terrible things, otherwise why would they keep them away from me.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
